snippet.title: Let's Play Final Fantasy II iOS (Gameplay + Walkthrough) Part 3 - Minwu's Aid
snippet.description:
Let's Play Final Fantasy II (iOS) Part 3 - After walking around Fynn and meeting Scott, we return to Altair and have Minwu join the party! We then head for the town of Paloom to sail towards Poft and we meet Cid.

If you've enjoyed the video, please like and share if you can! Thank you very much! ^-^
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DeltaShinyZeta/
